Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,# Down the Way 路途中
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 前奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}這忙碌的城鎮\NThis busy city
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.47,0:00:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我眼珠轉不來\Nblurs so swiftly by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.57,0:00:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}生命的交響曲\NSymphonies of lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}又一天開始\NThe new day arrives
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而我又停不住回想，我們從前\NAnd I can't stop from thinking about who we were
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}以為我知道家的處所\NThought I had known where home was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.12,0:00:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不在這，不在那\Nnot here, nor there
Comment: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:01:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而我也大可繼續夢想，以前過得怎樣\NAnd I can spend my time dreaming of the things that used to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}或繼續走這條長途\Nor travel down this long path
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一直在我眼前\Nthat's been out before me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而邊走邊看烏鴉，在路途中\NAnd going as the crow flies down the way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們的旅途從未終點，還有更多\Nour journey's never over, still follow down
